sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as 客户端
    participant Access as 接入层
    participant Orchestration as 编排层
    participant Data as 数据层
    participant Agent as Agent层
    participant Inference as 推理层
    participant Tool as 工具层
    Client->>Access: 发起请求
    activate Access
    Note right of Access: 验证 Token、解析请求体

    Access->>Orchestration: 转发请求
    deactivate Access
    activate Orchestration
    Note right of Orchestration: 创建 EventBus、ToolRegistry

    Orchestration->>Data: PlanStore 从后端加载行程计划
    activate Data
    Data-->>Orchestration: 返回行程计划
    deactivate Data

    Orchestration->>Agent: 创建 SupervisorAgent、SubAgentTool 列表
    activate Agent
    Agent-->>Orchestration: 返回实例
    deactivate Agent

    Note right of Orchestration: 启动后台 runner 任务

    Orchestration->>Inference: Supervisor LLM 循环
    activate Inference
    Note right of Inference: think → call tools

    loop 工具调用与子 Agent 循环
        Inference->>Tool: ToolRegistry 分发执行 (SubAgentTool.execute)
        activate Tool

        Tool->>Agent: 创建 Worker 实例
        activate Agent
        Agent-->>Tool: 返回 Worker 实例
        deactivate Agent

        Tool->>Inference: 触发 Worker LLM 循环
        activate Inference
        Inference->>Tool: Worker 调用 MCP 工具
        Tool-->>Inference: 返回工具执行结果
        deactivate Inference

        Tool-->>Inference: 结果回填到 Supervisor 消息
        deactivate Tool
    end

    Inference-->>Orchestration: Supervisor 输出最终回复
    deactivate Inference

    Note right of Orchestration: 发射 done 事件、关闭 EventBus

    Orchestration-->>Client: 前台协程逐条 yield SSE 事件 (SSE 流)
    deactivate Orchestration